						<summary>

						<p>Slab set up in front of the Śiva temple.</p>						

						<p>1435 A.D.</p>						

						<p>It is dated in Śaka 1357, Ānanda, Māgha ba. 14, Friday corresponding to January 13, Thursday f.d.t., °85, 1435, A.D.</p>						

						<p>Records the consecration of the image of Śrī Vīrabadradēva by Nāgārāju, the son of Cheṁgūmṭṭa Mallamarāju, of <hi rend="italic">Śaunaka gōtra</hi> and <hi rend="italic">Yajuś-śakha.</hi></p>						

						</summary>
